SMA Conference Update - Internet Announcement - 24 Aug 1994

The 8th Annual Meeting and Conference of the...

SOFTWARE MANAGEMENT ASSOCIATION (SMA)
The premier forum for software professionals who support
and manage existing software assets, SMA is noted for its
practical approach to discussing and solving software
development, maintenance, and management issues.

-- Presentations by experts in software management,
	development, maintenance, and project management
-- Perspectives from peers supporting a broad spectrum
	of industries
-- Networking with leading experts on major issues impacting
	quality, delivery, and maintenance of mission-
	critical systems
-- A forum to foster professional relationships
-- An opportunity to parlay conference participation into enhanced
	communication, vision, and organizational skills

Conference Theme:
Managing Software Assets in a Changing New World

8-11 Nov 1994, Phoenix, Arizona

